# Account Based Marketing Automation

We have automated the process of allowing you to send a manual first email whilst then having pre-set follow-up emails written and sent to the same prospects. 

This is a good approach when looking to be super-targeted and personalised whilst looking to automate follow ups so you don’t have to manage them manually

## **What is Account-Based Marketing?**

Account-based marketing is basically means sending manually written emails to prospects for the most effective results

